data.description: Wonderful Ranch Home with huge land, private long entry and a GORGEOUS MAGNIFICENT VIEW.  The sunset is phenomenal.  You have Panoramic 240 degree views from property of city lights, hills and mountains all around. Property is nested in the hills near Roy Kabian Memorial park which has 640 acres of trails to explore. This custom home is 4 bedroom 2 bath, BUILT IN 2006 and boasts views from every window. Kitchen opens up to family room. Floor plan boasts a large master suite with separate tub/shower & his/her sink, and walk-in closets.  The custom floor is amazing and contrasts very well with the home.   There is a part of the lot graded for a future 1200sqft home with a separate road entry (in case you'd like to build an additional home for passive income). Per seller, previous owner was going to build a 2nd home and a huge workshop.  The .  TAKE A LOOK!!!
